News Reelz: Jimmy Kimmel will be back to host the 90th annual Academy Awards!
.
.
The announcement puts this year’s Best Picture fiasco in the rearview mirror as the team behind the 89th Oscars reunites. Kimmel got solid reviews for his rookie turn as host of Hollywood’s Biggest Night in February, though the wild finale — La La Land mistakenly announced for the marquee trophy rather than proper winner Moonlight — is what people will remember most.
.
.
The host of ABC’s late-night staple Jimmy Kimmel Live! also hosted the Primetime Emmys last year and in 2012.
.
.
Happy to have him host again?
